You know. I think. "Oh. man.

551
00:26:12.805 --> 00:26:14.807
when this happens. he ain't
gonna be in a good mood."

552
00:26:14.874 --> 00:26:17.176
So the report card comes.

553
00:26:18.945 --> 00:26:21.247
My father.
he looked at this thing.

