571
00:27:07.093 --> 00:27:10.229
The door opens.
and my uncle is there.

572
00:27:10.296 --> 00:27:12.832
He said. "There's some
bad news for you. Donny."

573
00:27:12.899 --> 00:27:14.901
and he told me.

