00:28:46.692 --> 00:28:48.995
our country took
the challenge.

605
00:28:49.061 --> 00:28:50.629
so you describe how it was.

606
00:28:50.696 --> 00:28:54.266
- * Roll. Columbia.
won't you roll. roll. roll *

607
00:28:54.333 --> 00:28:55.835
- And each time.
"Roll on. Columbia."

608
00:28:55.902 --> 00:28:57.970
- * Won't you roll.
roll. roll *

